net.sf.jclal.gui.view.xml

Class GUIXmlConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jclal.gui.view.xml.GUIXmlConfig

  • public class GUIXmlConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class to load the properties needed to construct experiments. Can be used few files to config the experiment or all the elements can by in one file but the diferents elements types must be separated by at least one empty line.
    Author:
    Oscar Gabriel Reyes Pupo, Eduardo Perez Perdomo
